<h2 id="toc4"><span><strong>Lead Researcher:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmorris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2231487); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2231487&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1579869171" alt="DrMorris" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2231487)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmorris" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2231487); return false;">DrMorris</a></span></span></h2>
